source: TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCEHARD_00706_WAKADANNAOFMUJIKOZA_000_000<tab>I but moments ago finished poring over the first draft of our dear friend's latest epic. It paints a most fascinating picture of your adventures, filled with passion, suspense, fear, excitement─I could scarcely keep my heart from leaping from my breast!
target: TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCEHARD_00706_WAKADANNAOFMUJIKOZA_000_000<tab>Ich habe den ersten Entwurf gelesen und der war <var 1A 02 /var>spannend<var 1A 01 /var>! Deine Abenteuer haben mich zutiefst bewegt.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCEHARD_00706_WAKADANNAOFMUJIKOZA_000_001<tab>Oh, I can hardly wait to see how it ends. Thank you again for serving as the muse to his genius.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCEHARD_00706_WAKADANNAOFMUJIKOZA_000_001<tab>Ich werde hierbleiben und helfen, bis der letzte Akt des Stücks geschrieben ist. Und danke dir für die spannenden Geschichten!
